GET     /sponsor/                             SponsorController.List
GET     /sponsor/:id                           SponsorController.Read
PUT     /sponsor/:id                              SponsorController.Update
DELETE     /sponsor/:id                              SponsorController.Delete
GET     /show/sponsor/                             SponsorController.ShowList

# Videos
